{"tid":1734030,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"母親向警跪地痛哭 求見理大內子女","createTime":"2019-11-18T08:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T10:45:47.000Z","uid":46938,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8b6c47e8232a5fa96cdc06e8966b873e13daa34d","tid":1734030,"uid":46938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:38:05.000Z","msg":"約五六名家長稱他們的子女在理大內，他們走到尖東橋外，要求警方讓他們手牽手進內見子女一面。一名母親向警方跪地痛哭，稱「如果我個女死咗我跳樓畀你睇」；另一名家長要求見指揮官，讓他們入內，表示可以拘捕子女，不介意他們留案底，只求他們平安。有圍觀市民指罵警察，家長強調「我們只是和平，不要罵警」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一名女警用揚聲器稱家長挑釁人群，群眾即時表達不滿。家長現時於尖東橋口靜坐。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來源： <a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20191118/s00001/1574040265680/%e3%80%901118-%e7%90%86%e5%a4%a7%e3%80%91%e6%af%8d%e8%a6%aa%e5%90%91%e8%ad%a6%e8%b7%aa%e5%9c%b0%e7%97%9b%e5%93%ad-%e6%b1%82%e8%a6%8b%e7%90%86%e5%a4%a7%e5%85%a7%e5%ad%90%e5%a5%b3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191118%2Fs00001%2F1574040265680%2F%25e3%2580%25901118-%25e7%2590%2586%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25af%258d%25e8%25a6%25aa%25e5%2590%2591%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e8%25b7%25aa%25e5%259c%25b0%25e7%2597%259b%25e5%2593%25ad-%25e6%25b1%2582%25e8%25a6%258b%25e7%2590%2586%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%2585%25a7%25e5%25ad%2590%25e5%25a5%25b3&d=O2Kpqs6hAe%2BpM%2F1AUa5ix95k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=aae16a02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191118%2Fs00001%2F1574040265680%2F%25e3%2580%25901118-%25e7%2590%2586%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25af%258d%25e8%25a6%25aa%25e5%2590%2591%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e8%25b7%25aa%25e5%259c%25b0%25e7%2597%259b%25e5%2593%25ad-%25e6%25b1%2582%25e8%25a6%258b%25e7%2590%2586%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%2585%25a7%25e5%25ad%2590%25e5%25a5%25b3&h=7cc157b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.co